bug.author: pracheer
bug.description: The converter is able to successfully convert <denchmark-link:http://data.mxnet.io/models/imagenet/inception-bn/>Inception-BN</denchmark-link> model which we are able to use it in an iPhone app. But when we try to use <denchmark-link:http://data.mxnet.io/models/imagenet/inception-v3.tar.gz>InceptionV3</denchmark-link> model, the conversion goes through successfully but when run on the XCode simulator the screen goes blank. Note that <denchmark-link:https://developer.apple.com/machine-learning/>Apple's website</denchmark-link> lists some of the coreml models as examples and this list includes InceptionV3 hinting that our converted mxnet InceptionV3 model should also work.
